args:
Woooo! We finally got across the lake!
Now let's make like a bread wagon
and haul buns before the imperials
get away from us.
All units, ready yourself for an attack\non the nearby village! Crush all who\ndare to resist our might!
You're not gonna take this gorgeous lake\nOR the super adorable village!
Stand aside or be cut down, girl!
That's what I was gonna say to YOU!\n...Well, without the girl part.\nAnyway, get 'em, Lin!
What in blazes...? They're too strong to\nbe mere villagers!
Gya! They're holding the choke point\non this path! We can't get through!

Are you soldiers of the Empire or a group
of feckless wretches who are cowed by a
couple of children?! We have the superior
numbers, so OVERWHELM THEM ALREADY!
Girl, I think these losers are\ntotally underestimating us.
Exactly! Now let's show 'em what we can\ndo when we fight together and stuff!
How...how can they be so strong...?!\nWe've lost dozens of men already!
Yeah, they're totally throwing everything\nthey got at us—but we still won't let 'em\ntake over this village!
Enough! I will deal with these two\npersonally. Commander, take the rest\nof the men and skirt around the lake.
Understood, sir. ...All units,\nfall back and regroup!
No! They're gonna hit the village\nfrom the other direction!
Oh man, this SUCKS! Okay, we're\ngonna chase 'em down and—
No, little ones. You will not.
Not for long—we're gonna knock that\nsmug look right off his stupid face!
No! The imperial soldiers are here!
There's too many—we'll never be able\nto hide. ...Come here, child!
Listen to me: Mama and Papa are going\nto stay here and distract the bad men.\nYou have to run. Do you hear me? RUN.
There's some over there, too!\nA man and a woman, plus a kid!\nCapture them!
Don't look back. Just run. And remember\nthat we will always love you!
I'm sorry we couldn't stop 'em from\ninvading your village, but we're here\nto kick 'em out now!
Lin, can you go after that little girl?\nShe'll never be able to outrun the\nsoldiers on those tiny little legs.
I've totally got it. You just go.
You can't fight this many soldiers\non your own.
Don't worry—you aren't the only one\nwhose dad taught her a few tricks!
He showed me how to use a spear,\nso I'm totally gonna turn these dopes\ninto swiss cheese!
You just go save the kid.
Ha ha! Girl, you know I will be!
You caught up to us faster\nthan I was anticipating...
Still, it was foolish of you to split off\nfrom your companion. Prepare to die!
Oh, I didn't split off from anything—\nLin and me are a united front!
We talked together, fought together,\nrode a freakin' BOAT together...
This place is crammed full\nof memories for both of us.
So as long as I'm fighting here,\nI'll NEVER be alone!
Your foolish talk of memories will mean\nlittle when you are bleeding to death\non the cobblestones. ...Kill her, men!
I KNEW you guys were underestimating us!
